data.description: Whether you are looking for a vacation home or your first home, this is the place! 2018 built Fleetwood home featuring 2 large bedrooms. Come into the home via a large covered front porch, with a welcoming hand carved bench. Enjoy sitting looking out on your great green space, enjoy everything Timberlakes has to offer. Easy care Vinyl plank flooring throughout. The large carport, Tuffshed, and even the BBQ stay, meaning you can move in and enjoy!
